name: Push-up
description: Push up your body with arms which keeping your legs and back straight.

name: Sit-up
description: Lie on your back on the floor and rouse the top part your body to a sitting position.

name: Plunk
description: A long narrow flat piece of wood that is used for making floors, etc.

name: Stretch
description: An act of stretching out your arms or legs or your body and contracting the muscles.

name: Pull-up
description: An exercise in which you hold onto a high bar above your head and pull up towards it.

name: Jogging
description: The activity of running at a show regular speed, especially as a form of exercise.

name: Jumping jacks
description: Sometimes in a clap, and then returning to a position with the feet together.

name: Warm-up
description: A warm-up is important before a run so as not to strain any muscles.

name: Barbell
description: Tool used in weight training, bodybuilding, weightlifting with weights attached.
